@startuml
title Timing Diagram - Example

concise "Sensor" as Sensor
concise "Controller" as Controller

@0
Sensor is Idle
Controller is Idle

@20
Sensor is Active : Detects event
Sensor -> Controller : Signal

@40
Controller is Active : Handle event
Controller -> Controller : Update state

@80
Controller is Idle
Sensor is Idle

@90
note right of Controller
	Example timing flow
end note

@enduml